Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Final Decision (Episode 25)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On the morning of April 27th, the UK, the US, and China announced a trilateral joint declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Potsdam Declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, Kantaro Suzuki, the president of the Information Bureau of the Cabinet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hiroshi Shimomura admired the strength of the little bird that came to seek food even in the scorched earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mr. Oyadomari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Important news has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Important news?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At 6 o'clock this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,San Francisco reported a declaration from the United States, the United Kingdom, and China.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The US, UK, and China? Isn't it the US, UK, and the Soviet Union?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is in the US, UK and China. surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They demand unconditional surrender by Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It consists of 13 items.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is almost the same as the Cairo Declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. What do you think? Not as an information officer, but as an individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the same as an individual and an Army intelligence officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE {or just him making a questioning noise}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you read it carefully, it is very hard on the war leaders, but respects the people and human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a ploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They are calling for surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you surrender to the US, UK, and China?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the current leadership, no one has the courage to respond to this surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know it's time to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:04:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Army is in a thorough fight, and the Cabinet is trying to avoid responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, we lose our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not only our chance, but more and more people are being killed while we dither.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The United States, dropped leaflets sown with bombs to inform the Japanese people of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the cabinet decided to portray this proclamation as a plot to upset the people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and claim that the United States was impatient to collect its own station as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,However, perhaps this problem is too well known to kill silently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be suspicious to publish this important news in the newspaper without knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it? If so, I will respect the minister's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is announced, it should be categorically criticized
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to prevent morale from deteriorating, and raise the fighting spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that would ruin the peace work that is currently underway through the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you still doing peace work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do not show your will to fight to the end, you cannot even make peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the Soviet Union attending the Potsdam Conference, the Japanese government was still hoping for a peace treaty
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,through the Soviet Union and was negotiating through dispatches to Fumimaro Konoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Harry, Chief of Information for the United States, has declared that:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire population of Japan has become a front-line military target.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no non-combatants in Japan now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We seek to destroy the largest number of enemies, both men and women, in the shortest possible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite this, the Japanese people are unaware of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we need to let them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In that regard, if you have any reason to oppose this, at your own discretion, please let me know in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nuisance to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, What is nuisance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The people are happy to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you are a private actor, you do not feel worried about the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't work for you anymore. Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the mainland will be a battlefield, it will kill all the old people, children, and sick ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anyone who is going to be more of a stumbling block
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,than commanders of the Japanese army who says such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they, want to kill all our people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to underline this claim, another calamity fell on the innocent people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,who are killed by both their enemies and allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At 8:15 a.m. on August 6th, 1945, the atomic bomb was dropped on Hiroshima for the first time in human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In an instant, 240,000 people were killed or injured there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A plutonium bomb was also dropped on Nagasaki around 11:00 a.m. on August 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here again, more than 100,000 people died in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What surprised the Japanese commanders more than that was the actions of the Soviet Union,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,which Japan had requested to mediate peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly they had declared that they would participate in the war against Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The first Cabinet meeting since then was held on August 9th at 14:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After explaining the current situation to Foreign Minister Togo, Prime Minister Kantaro Suzuki stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As Foreign Minister Togo said, things have become desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:09:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask all of you for your opinions and to decide on a policy regarding the Tripartite Joint Declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,At present, no matter how much the three allied countries talk about the security of the imperial family
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and give favorable conditions, unconditional surrender is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, with the atomic bomb and war with the Soviet Union, there is no prospect of victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As we continue to fight for the honor of the Yamato people, we will have some chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask for the people's cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come up with a tactic, I think there is a possibility that the battlefield situation will improve
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than us being completely defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the chance of that? In particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A decisive battle on the mainland!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Only then will you have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to give the Army a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, modern warfare cannot be done without the total backing of the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a war that the Army or the Navy alone can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Prior to the the atomic bomb and the entering of the Soviet Union,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there was no material for the war to continue in the current domestic situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the Navy has no chance of winning against the US and UK.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, I am not particular about honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to stop this wishful thinking and have discussions in line with the actual situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, regarding whether or not to accept the Trilateral Joint Declaration,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the group wanting to accept with Foreign Minister Togo and the Navy Minister Yonai
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and the opposition group with the Minister of the Army, Anan, and the Minister of Munitions Toyoda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,will discuss long after 22:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no conclusion could be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened to the Cabinet decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't come to a conclusion yet?.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what about you, Governor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to accept or do you oppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a personal opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm spokesman for the cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my job to give an opinion on behalf of the cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,More than that, when I came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was taught by looking at the cycads in front of the entrance of the Prime Ministers Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That big cycad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it was destroyed by air raids, and the leaves and trees were destroyed in bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I look at it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that blue sprouts are emerging from among the burnt trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japanese people are cycads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, someday new buds will come out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't take the root.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to leave them in any form!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I will go soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From 23:50, the Supreme War Leaders’ Meeting will be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to kill the buds even a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In the palace? Then, is it an Imperial Conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There are cycads here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, from 23:50 on August 9th, an Imperial Conference was convened to ask for the Emperor's decision and decree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The appearance of the ministers at the Supreme Council varies,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but their thoughts were just the result of the Imperial Conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Shimomura, I would like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the Emperor ever been asked for his decree like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, even though it was a sacred decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it was said that the opinions summarized by his vassals would be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty the emperor himself has not made a decision like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a lot of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. After all. It is unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:14:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The decision the people have made so far will be painful,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, what kind of story did you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cycad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's what you were talking about at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, no matter what happens to the old leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if the roots are not withered, new shoots will come out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens to the old leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supreme War Leaders Conference is now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we will hold a cabinet meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Each member gave their opinions one by one, and after that, we received a sacred decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The gist of the words is that when looking at the situation in the nation, continuing the war not only destroys Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but also makes the world's human beings even more unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he would accept the three countries declaration, and end the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, his Majesty had words of compassion for the Army and Navy soldiers, casualties, and victims of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus the decree came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,However, some members of the Army and Navy have voiced opposition to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this decision regarding the conditions under which they would accept the Tripartite Joint Declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, on the 14th, an Imperial conference was held again with the attendance of all ministers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and unconditional surrender was finally decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for the last time. Is this the original plan of an imperial edict?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It is quite difficult to want everyone in the nation to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what will happen when the imperial decision comes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you announce it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Newspapers and radio broadcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do both, so it will be up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That One
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Jewel Voice Broadcasting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Some officers are aiming to prevent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Thank you for letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take some measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no countermeasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is his Majesty's life-threatening decree, then I will protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,During this time, when I received his Majesty's decree, I was deeply impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This final decision is life-threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time of the final decision, there will be a lot of commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that you can always make a decision to return to the beginning if you risk your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I also made a lot of noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,However, everyone thinks it's good for the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are many things that are good for the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the decision of the highest officer to make no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your future life-threatening job to convey his Majesty's words to the Japanese people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,10:00 a.m. on August 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An unprecedented event in Japanese history the "Jewel Voice Broadcast" was recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yabe, you and I are the only ones who controlled the recording board
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the basement of the Imperial Household Ministry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,#MISSING LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be caught tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wont talk even if it costs my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to break either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the Minister of State Shimomuria?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,take him to the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi Shimomura?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought Hiroshi Shimomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Hiroshi Shimomura, the president of the Information Bureau, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been checking the car now, but I didn't find the recording board for Jewel Voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want that recording board?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want His Majesty to spend another three or four days thinking it over and that His Majesty can trust the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that in three or four days?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me anyways. Where is the recording board?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, would you like me to search your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, Governor Shimomura was fearful for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, he envisioned a defensive mainland operation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,at the behest of the Minister of the Imperial Japanese Army Anan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Life-threatening alone is not an accurate decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the decision of the highest level?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to deal with Governor Shimomura now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't open his mouth anyway, so go look for it at the Imperial Household Ministry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep all of them in this place until we finish the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They urged the Broadcasting Association, Director Yabe, to take him to the back of the Imperial Household Ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask where the recording board was, but he didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, some rebel officers invaded the broadcasting station before dawn on the 15th and tried to broadcast
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by themselves, but they did not succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They pulled up to the imperial palace and decided to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,<The Jewel Voice Broadcast>\N#LINE 1 {Full translation here https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hirohito_surrender_broadcast}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"enduring the unendurable and suffering what is insufferable."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,#LINE 2
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,#LINE 3
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,#LINE 4
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,#LINE 5
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, the superlative decision was life-threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But that alone does not seem to make a real decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was fearful of course, His Majesty, Anan, Yoneuchi, and Togo as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is everyone making a different decision although they are all fearful?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference is the protection of the national polity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we say "Japan", it exists because the country and the people remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't grasped this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a country, there is no national polity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's important to keep that country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If only the country is left,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan will surely sprout again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an eye that looks closely at the theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it is important to look forward to the future without being bound by your own position.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And a courageous one.
